    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-1a' );" name="002-1a" class="pb">[002-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:198'>　禹貢㑹箋卷二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='198:219'>　　　　　　　　　　翰林院檢討徐文靖撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='219:239'>濟河惟兗州<span class='krp-note'>漢書濟作泲/史記兗作沇</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='239:263'>　蔡𫝊曰兗州之域東南據濟西北距河蘇氏曰河濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='263:289'>　之間相去不逺兗州之境東南跨濟非止於濟也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='289:312'>　按正義曰濟河之間相去路近兗州之境跨濟而過</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='312:335'>　東南越濟水西北至東河也羅平曰九州之界濟河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='335:361'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-1b' );" name="002-1b" class="pb">[002-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='361:396'>　<span class='krp-note'>兗/</span>淮岱<span class='krp-note'>徐/</span>相去不能千里荆河<span class='krp-note'>豫/</span>千里而贏海岱<span class='krp-note'>青/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='396:425'>　千里而縮荆山衡陽<span class='krp-note'>荆/</span>二千里而遥東海西河<span class='krp-note'>冀/</span>二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='425:451'>　千里而近壽春之淮潮陽之海<span class='krp-note'>揚/</span>相去五六千里龍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='451:480'>　門之河燉煌之黑<span class='krp-note'>雍/</span>相去且四千里華陽黒水<span class='krp-note'>梁/</span>窮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='480:503'>　數千里猶未知其所終荆河淮濟之間斷長補短不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='503:521'>　能淮海一州之半則知所制各有當矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='521:527'>九河既道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='527:551'>　蔡𫝊曰九河爾雅一曰徒駭二曰太史三曰馬頰四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='551:577'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-2a' );" name="002-2a" class="pb">[002-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='577:600'>　曰覆鬴五曰胡蘇六曰簡潔七曰鈎盤八曰鬲津其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='600:623'>　一則河之經流也先儒不知河之經流遂分簡潔為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='623:649'>　二既道既順其道也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按爾雅簡潔郭璞曰簡水道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='649:672'>　簡易絜水多約絜朱子注孟亦分簡潔為二又呉氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='672:696'>　程曰南皮縣明有簡河何嘗合絜為一蔡𫝊乃合簡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='696:719'>　絜而一之非也邢昺曰九河所在徒駭最北鬲津最</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='719:742'>　南葢徒駭是河之本道東出分為八枝也然則徒駭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='742:764'>　即河之經流蔡𫝊謂徒駭而外别有一經流非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='764:790'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-2b' );" name="002-2b" class="pb">[002-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='790:814'>　𫝊又曰按徒駭河地志云滹沱河寰宇記云在滄州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='814:840'>　清池南許商云在成平<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按唐地志滄州清池縣有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='840:863'>　徒駭河九域志在故滄州廢清池縣西北二十里寰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='863:887'>　宇記在清池縣西五十里𫝊云南誤邢昺爾雅疏九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='887:910'>　河所在徒駭最北鬲津最南葢徒駭是河之本道東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='910:934'>　北分為八枝也然則徒駭即河之經流𫝊云徒駭而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='934:954'>　外别有所為經流者以簡絜誤合而為一也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='954:978'>　𫝊又曰馬頰河元和志云在德州安德平原東南寰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='978:1004'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-3a' );" name="002-3a" class="pb">[002-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1004:1030'>　宇記云在棣州商河北輿地記云即篤馬河也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1030:1053'>　溝洫志孫禁以為可開通大河今入故篤馬河先儒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1053:1076'>　以為即馬頰唐地志德州平昌縣有馬頰河金史志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1076:1099'>　棣州商河縣有馬頰河一統志馬頰河在東光縣界</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1099:1122'>　經堂邑清平二縣界東達樂陵入海又髙唐州西有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1122:1130'>　馬頰河故道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1130:1157'>　𫝊又曰覆鬴河通典云在德州安德<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按一統志覆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1157:1173'>　鬴枯河自慶雲經海豐縣南入海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1173:1199'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-3b' );" name="002-3b" class="pb">[002-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1199:1223'>　𫝊又曰胡蘇河寰宇記云在滄之饒安無棣臨津三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1223:1249'>　縣許商云在東光<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按許商謂古説九河之名有徒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1249:1272'>　駭胡蘇鬲津今現在成平東光鬲縣界中郡國志勃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1272:1295'>　海東光縣有胡蘇亭胡蘇河水經注清河又東至東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1295:1318'>　光縣西南逕胡蘇亭又東北右㑹大河故瀆元史云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1318:1336'>　胡蘇在慶雲西南<span class='krp-note'>廣雲故/無棣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1336:1363'>　𫝊又曰簡潔河輿地記云在臨津<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按方輿紀要絜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1363:1386'>　與簡相近輿地記云在臨津孔氏謂在貝州厯亭縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1386:1412'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-4a' );" name="002-4a" class="pb">[002-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1412:1435'>　誤也金史南皮縣有絜河元志簡潔在南皮城外十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1435:1440'>　餘步</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1440:1464'>　𫝊又曰鉤盤河寰宇記云在樂陵東南從德州平昌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1464:1495'>　來<span class='krp-note'>今徳/平縣</span>輿地記云在樂陵<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按水經注般縣般河葢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1495:1518'>　亦九河之一也漢書稱公孫瓚破黄巾於般河即此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1518:1536'>　瀆也元志獻縣東南八十里有鉤盤河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1536:1560'>　𫝊曰鬲津河寰宇記云在樂陵東西北流入饒安許</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1560:1586'>　商云在鬲縣輿地記云在無棣<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按溝洫志許商以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1586:1612'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-4b' );" name="002-4b" class="pb">[002-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1612:1635'>　為古説九河之名有徒駭胡蘇鬲津今見在成平東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1635:1658'>　光鬲界中自鬲以北至徒駭間相去二百餘里今河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1658:1681'>　雖數移徙不離此域方輿紀要鬲津在鉤盤之北漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1681:1704'>　志注平原鬲縣平當以為鬲津通典在獻縣之廢饒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1704:1727'>　安縣元志在慶雲縣又在樂陵縣西三十里一統志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1727:1736'>　云至海豐入海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1736:1763'>　𫝊曰太史河不知所在<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按通典曰九河四在景成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1763:1786'>　二在平原其太史簡絜未詳處所方輿紀要太史河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1786:1812'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-5a' );" name="002-5a" class="pb">[002-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1812:1831'>　在徒駭之東元志太史河在南皮縣治北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1831:1855'>　𫝊又曰九河水道變遷難於推考而碣石通頂趾皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1855:1878'>　石不應仆没今兗冀之地既無此石而平州正南有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1878:1901'>　山而名碣石者尚在海中去岸五百餘里卓立可見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1901:1924'>　則是古河自今以為海處向北斜行始分為九其河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1924:1947'>　已淪於海明矣漢王横言昔天常連雨東北風海水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1947:1970'>　溢西南出浸數百里九河之地已為海水所漸酈道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1970:1993'>　元亦言九河碣石苞淪於海後世儒者知求九河於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1993:2019'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-5b' );" name="002-5b" class="pb">[002-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2019:2042'>　平地而不知求碣石有無以為之證故前後異説究</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2042:2068'>　無歸宿<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按封禪書北至碣石巡自遼西地理志碣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2068:2091'>　石在驪成西南今永平昌黎縣北相去二十里現有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2091:2114'>　碣石何得云去岸五百里也自石晉以幽薊十六州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2114:2137'>　賂契丹厯宋數百年足跡未至其地近自滄州望平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2137:2160'>　州約五百餘里何得以碣石逺在海中去平州五百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2160:2183'>　里也縱使去平州五百餘里又何得有卓立可見者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2183:2206'>　水經注曰禹貢兗州九河既道矣謂徒駭太史馬頰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2206:2232'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-6a' );" name="002-6a" class="pb">[002-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2232:2255'>　覆鬴胡蘇簡潔鈎盤鬲津也同為逆河葢所潤下之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2255:2279'>　𫝑以通河海及齊桓霸世塞廣田居同為一河故自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2279:2310'>　堰以北館陶廮陶<span class='krp-note'>唐志趙州寧/晉本廮陶丘</span>貝丘鬲般廣光信都</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2310:2333'>　東光河間樂成城地並存川瀆多亡漢世河决金隄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2333:2356'>　南北離其害議者欲求九河故迹而川之未知其所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2356:2379'>　夫欲求九河故迹則必有故迹之處可求豈謂求之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2379:2402'>　於海乎孫禁謂開通大河令入故篤馬河至海五百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2402:2425'>　里豈謂至碣石五百里乎至王横言天常連雨東北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2425:2451'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-6b' );" name="002-6b" class="pb">[002-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2451:2475'>　風海水溢西南浸數百里如春秋所書宋大水𩔖豈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2475:2490'>　風息雨霽之後宋遂淪為海乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2490:2496'>雷夏既澤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2496:2520'>　蔡𫝊曰澤水之鍾也雷夏地志在濟隂郡成陽縣西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2520:2543'>　北今濮州雷澤縣西北也山海經云澤中有雷神龍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2543:2566'>　身而人頭鼓其腹則雷然則本夏澤也因其神名之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2566:2592'>　曰雷夏也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按山海經雷澤有雷神龍身而人頭鼓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2592:2615'>　其腹在呉西漢地志㑹稽呉縣具區在西古文以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2615:2641'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-7a' );" name="002-7a" class="pb">[002-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2641:2664'>　震澤郡國志呉郡呉縣震澤在西劉昭注曰越絶書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2664:2687'>　云湖周三萬六千頃有大雷山小雷山水經注太湖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2687:2710'>　有大雷小雷三山亦謂之三山湖此雷澤即震澤與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2710:2734'>　禹貢雷夏無涉蔡𫝊之誤因史遷舜紀舜漁雷澤正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2734:2757'>　義曰雷澤有雷神鼓其腹則雷改經文在呉西字為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2757:2780'>　則雷字而不知其非禹貢之雷澤也据漢地志曰濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2780:2803'>　隂定陶詩風曹國也堯作游成陽舜漁雷澤故其民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2803:2826'>　猶有先王之遺風括地志曰雷夏在濮州雷澤縣郭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2826:2852'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-7b' );" name="002-7b" class="pb">[002-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2852:2875'>　外西北元和志曰雷澤縣西北至濮州九十里此則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2875:2898'>　禹貢之雷澤矣近志云雷澤東西二十里南北十五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2898:2921'>　里李之藻云澤底有巉石深壑冬至前水吸而入如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2921:2944'>　巨雷鳴故名雷澤意洪水懷襄之世雷澤未陂泛濫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2944:2968'>　彌廣史稱舜漁於雷澤就時於負夏鄭𤣥曰負夏衛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2968:2991'>　地孫奭孟子疏曰今之東郡是也意是時雷澤負夏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2991:3014'>　或皆其澤所瀰漫故總名雷夏未可知也正義曰洪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='3014:3037'>　水之時高原亦水澤不為澤雷夏既澤高地水盡此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='3037:3063'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-8a' );" name="002-8a" class="pb">[002-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='3063:3086'>　復為澤也周禮稻人職曰凡稼澤夏以水殄草而芟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='3086:3101'>　夷之澤草所生種之芒種是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='3101:3107'>灉沮㑹同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='3107:3130'>　蔡傳曰灉水曾氏曰爾雅水自河出為灉許氏曰河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3130:3153'>　灉水在宋水經汳水出隂溝東至蒙為狙獾灉水即</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3153:3179'>　汳水也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按元和志曰灉水沮水二源俱出雷澤縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3179:3202'>　西北平地去縣十四里許氏曰灉水東入泗下流入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3202:3225'>　沮韓氏謂此乃河之别流在豫州者東厯徐州境入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3225:3251'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-8b' );" name="002-8b" class="pb">[002-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3251:3274'>　泗水經汳水出隂溝於浚儀縣北東至梁郡蒙縣為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3274:3298'>　濉水𫉬水出汳水於梁郡蒙縣北又東至彭城縣北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3298:3317'>　東入於泗蔡傳狙獾乃沮𫉬二字之譌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3317:3340'>　蔡傳曰晁氏曰爾雅自河出為灉濟出為濋求之於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3340:3367'>　韻沮有楚音<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按僖十九年左𫝊注杜預曰沮水受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3367:3390'>　汴東經陳留梁譙沛彭城縣入泗水經瓠子河出東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3390:3413'>　郡濮陽縣北河注曰禹貢灉沮㑹同許慎曰河灉水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3413:3436'>　也九域志曰濮州有沮溝即禹貢灉沮㑹同者京相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3436:3462'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-9a' );" name="002-9a" class="pb">[002-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3462:3485'>　璠曰今濮陽城西南十五里有沮丘城六國時沮楚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3485:3495'>　同以為楚丘非也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3495:3501'>桑土既蠶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3501:3525'>　蔡𫝊曰蠶性惡濕故水退而後可蠶然九州皆賴其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3525:3548'>　利而獨於兗言之者兗地宜桑後世之濮上桑間猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3548:3574'>　可驗也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按祭義曰古者天子諸侯必有公桑蠶室</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3574:3597'>　大昕之朝桑於公桑風戾以食之鄭氏曰風戾之使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3597:3620'>　露氣燥乃以食蠶蠶性惡濕是也秦少游蠶書序略</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3620:3646'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-9b' );" name="002-9b" class="pb">[002-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3646:3670'>　曰考之禹貢揚梁冀雍不貢繭物兗篚織文徐篚𤣥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3670:3694'>　纖縞荆篚𤣥纁璣組豫篚纖縞青篚檿絲皆繭物也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3694:3717'>　而桑土既蠶獨言於兗然則九州蠶事兗為最乎夏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3717:3742'>　小正三月攝桑𫝊曰桑攝而記之急桑也貨殖𫝊齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3742:3766'>　魯千𣗳桑與千户侯等詩邶鄘衛譜東及兗州桑土</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3766:3789'>　之野正義曰今濮水之上地有桑間者是有桑土明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3789:3793'>　矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3793:3810'>是降丘宅土<span class='krp-note'>史記作下/一居土</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3810:3837'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-10a' );" name="002-10a" class="pb">[002-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3837:3861'>　蔡𫝊曰兗地多在卑下水害尤甚民皆依丘陵以居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3861:3887'>　至是始得下居平地也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按鄭氏曰此州寡於山而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3887:3910'>　夾川兩大流之間遭洪水其民尤困水害既除於是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3910:3933'>　下丘居土以其免於厄尤喜故記之周官大司徒以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3933:3956'>　土宜之法辨十有二土之名物以相民宅而知其利</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3956:3979'>　害注曰相視其地以奠民居使知趨利避害各得其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3979:4002'>　所也當日禹作司空掌邦土居四民時地利正其事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='4002:4025'>　也是降丘宅土非止為下居平地故於蠶桑既興後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='4025:4052'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-10b' );" name="002-10b" class="pb">[002-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='4052:4057'>　記之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='4057:4063'>厥土黑墳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='4063:4091'>　蔡𫝊曰土脉墳起也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按孔𫝊曰色黑而墳起陸氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='4091:4114'>　釋文曰馬云有肥澤也周禮草人職墳壤用麋援神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='4114:4138'>　契曰黑墳宜種麥説卦𫝊坤於地為黑兗土乃黑而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='4138:4143'>　墳也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='4143:4153'>厥草惟繇厥木惟條</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4153:4177'>　蔡𫝊曰林氏曰兗徐揚三州最居東南下流其地卑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4177:4204'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-11a' );" name="002-11a" class="pb">[002-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4204:4227'>　濕沮洳洪水為患草木不得其生至是或繇或條或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4227:4253'>　夭或喬而或漸包故於三州特言之<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按論衡曰地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4253:4276'>　性生草山性生木故草木於山為宜兗州寡於山而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4276:4299'>　夾以河濟之間水盛而草木不生今既長茂故特書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4299:4323'>　之孔𫝊曰繇茂條長馬云繇抽也坤文言曰天地變</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4323:4334'>　化草木蕃其謂是乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4334:4344'>厥田惟中下厥賦貞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4344:4368'>　蔡𫝊曰貞正也兗賦最薄言君天下者以薄賦為正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4368:4395'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-11b' );" name="002-11b" class="pb">[002-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4395:4421'>　也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按隋書食志云采制九等而康歌興九州以土</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4421:4444'>　色定田皆有定賦惟冀豫梁揚錯出冀豫荆青徐雍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4444:4467'>　兗揚梁為次然雍兗皆六六而無九今兗田第六賦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4467:4490'>　亦第六無復下上之别故曰貞鄭氏曰貞正也其賦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4490:4513'>　中上則是田正與賦相當故以為貞也周書無逸所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4513:4537'>　謂惟正之供蔡𫝊云以薄賦為正其餘八州之賦將</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4537:4546'>　遂不得為正乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4546:4555'>作十有三載乃同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4555:4582'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-12a' );" name="002-12a" class="pb">[002-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4582:4606'>　蔡𫝊曰兗當河下流之衝今水患雖平而卑濕沮洳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4606:4629'>　未必盡去土曠人稀生理鮮少必治作十有三載然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4629:4655'>　後賦法同於他州<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按鄭氏曰治此州正作不休十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4655:4678'>　三年乃有賦與八州同言功難也夫以為治此州者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4678:4701'>　正作不休則貞作連讀可乎且十三年中八州有賦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4701:4724'>　而兗獨無其果然乎意以作當為耕作如冀州大陸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4724:4748'>　既作之𩔖葢兗田第六賦亦第六必耕作十有三載</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4748:4771'>　貞問其田之收穫賦之正供無復有上下豐歉之異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4771:4798'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-12b' );" name="002-12b" class="pb">[002-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4798:4821'>　故曰貞也若以為同於他州則兗賦第六他州亦第</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4821:4844'>　六乎然必十有三載者周禮天府職云季冬陳玉以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4844:4867'>　貞來嵗之媺惡鄭氏曰問事之正曰貞問嵗之媺惡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4867:4890'>　謂問於龜太卜職太貞之屬史記太隂在子旱明嵗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4890:4913'>　美至卯穰明歳衰惡至午旱明歳美至酉穰明歳衰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4913:4936'>　惡故必十三載乃可以同周職方曰兗州其榖宜四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4936:4940'>　種</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4940:4946'>厥貢漆絲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4946:4973'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-13a' );" name="002-13a" class="pb">[002-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4973:5000'>　蔡𫝊曰兗地宜漆宜桑故貢漆絲也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按禇遂良曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='5000:5023'>　舜造漆器禹雕其俎是漆為當時器用之所需也貨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='5023:5047'>　殖𫝊山東多魚鹽漆絲故兗貢之考工記㡛人湅絲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='5047:5070'>　以涚水漚其絲鄭氏曰涗水謂以灰所泲水也楚人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='5070:5079'>　曰漚齊人曰涹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='5079:5093'>厥篚織文<span class='krp-note'>漢書篚/作棐</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='5093:5117'>　蔡𫝊曰篚竹器筐屬也古者幣帛之屬則盛之以筐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='5117:5143'>　篚而貢焉織文者織而有文錦綺之屬也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按三禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='5143:5170'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-13b' );" name="002-13b" class="pb">[002-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='5170:5193'>　圖曰篚以竹為之長三尺廣一尺深三寸足高三寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='5193:5217'>　上有葢孔𫝊曰地宜漆林又宜桑蠶織文錦綺之屬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='5217:5240'>　盛之筐篚而貢焉据禮記深衣士不衣織鄭注曰織</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='5240:5263'>　染絲織之士衣染繒也是織文乃染絲織之而有文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='5263:5286'>　非必為錦綺也詩六月織文鳥章又周禮玉府掌王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='5286:5309'>　之獻文織良貨賄之屬注曰文織謂織之有文出於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='5309:5322'>　織成者其非為錦綺可知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='5322:5341'>浮於濟漯達于河<span class='krp-note'>史記漢書/濟作泲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='5341:5368'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-14a' );" name="002-14a" class="pb">[002-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='5368:5392'>　蔡𫝊曰舟行水曰浮漯者河之枝流也兗之貢賦浮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='5392:5418'>　濟浮漯以達於河也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按水經曰濟水又東北過甲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='5418:5441'>　下邑入於河酈注曰山海經濟水入鉅野注渤海入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='5441:5464'>　濟琅槐東北者也又東北河水枝津注之水經以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='5464:5487'>　入河非也斯乃河水注濟非濟入河杜佑曰濟水因</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='5487:5510'>　王莽末渠涸不復截河過今東平濟南淄川北海界</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='5510:5533'>　中有水流入海謂之清河實菏澤汶水合流亦曰濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='5533:5556'>　河葢因舊名非濟水也郭景純曰濟自滎陽至樂安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5556:5583'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-14b' );" name="002-14b" class="pb">[002-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5583:5606'>　博昌入海今河竭濟水仍流不絶然河水於濟漯之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5606:5629'>　北别流注海今所輟流者惟漯水耳郭或以為濟注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5629:5651'>　之事實非也孔𫝊曰順流曰浮因水入水曰達</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5651:5675'>　蔡𫝊曰地志漯水出東郡東武陽至千乗入海程氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5675:5698'>　以為此乃漢河與漯殊異然亦不能明言漯河所在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5698:5724'>　未詳其地也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按水經注曰桑欽地理志漯水出髙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5724:5748'>　唐余按穆天子𫝊丁夘天子自五鹿東征釣於漯水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5748:5771'>　以祭淑人己巳天子東征食馬於漯水之上尋其沿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5771:5798'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-15a' );" name="002-15a" class="pb">[002-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5798:5822'>　歴逕趣不得近出高唐也据穆𫝊郭注漯水今濟隂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5822:5845'>　漯隂縣是漯隂在濟水之隂也水經漯水逕高唐縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5845:5868'>　故城東又東北逕漯隂故城北故兗州貢賦浮濟浮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5868:5891'>　漯以入河也金史志博州博平縣有漯河今在章丘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5891:5914'>　縣東北七里源出縣之長白山西北流入小清河唐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5914:5937'>　志濟南章丘縣有長白山是也薛氏謂古漯自東昌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5937:5960'>　府朝城縣受河而東入海故浮漯可以達河西漢末</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5960:5983'>　河并行漯川其後河徙而漯亦不復存矣章丘縣志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5983:6010'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '002-15b' );" name="002-15b" class="pb">[002-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='6010:6033'>　縣東北七里有漯水出長山縣之長白山西北流入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='6033:6043'>　小清河非古漯也</span><br/>
